## Mécanisme 2 — Clé SSH (Secret handshake)

```bash
ls -la /home/zeroday/.ssh/
cat /home/zeroday/.ssh/.authorized_keys
```

```
ecdsa-sha2-nistp256 AAAA...BGA= 326e6420706172743a20755f6730745f.local
